---
import CliPreview from "./cli";
import PageSection from "./pageSection.astro";
---

<PageSection
  className="mx-auto grid max-w-7xl grid-cols-1 items-center gap-8 px-4 pb-12 sm:px-6 lg:grid lg:gap-x-8 lg:px-8 xl:grid-cols-2 xl:gap-x-12"
  size={"24"}
  id="about"
>
  <div class="mx-auto flex max-w-[800px] flex-col gap-2 md:gap-4 xl:max-w-full">
    <h2
      class="mb-2 w-full text-3xl font-bold text-t3-purple-50 md:text-5xl lg:text-5xl"
    >
      Build on Aztec
    </h2>
    <p
      class="mx-auto mt-4 max-w-3xl text-base text-t3-purple-200 md:text-xl lg:text-xl xl:text-xl"
    >
      We created create-aztec-dapp to streamline the setup of Aztec applications with an emphasis on developer experience and best practices.
    </p>
    <p
      class="mx-auto mt-4 max-w-3xl text-base text-t3-purple-200 md:text-xl lg:text-xl xl:text-xl"
    >
      Aztec provides powerful privacy-focused solutions for your blockchain applications, and this CLI helps you get started quickly.
    </p>
    <p
      class="mx-auto mt-4 max-w-3xl text-base text-t3-purple-200 md:text-xl lg:text-xl xl:text-xl"
    >
      This starter kit includes everything you need to build and deploy your first Aztec dApp with confidence.
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="min-h-[300px] md:min-h-[400px]">
    <CliPreview client:only="react" />
  </div>
</PageSection>
